&gt;&gt; How was the Millennium Stage
last night, how was your gig there?

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:16.140
&gt;&gt; It was great.

00:04:16.140 --> 00:04:17.440
&gt;&gt; It was really good.

00:04:17.440 --> 00:04:18.740
&gt;&gt; Yeah?

00:04:18.740 --> 00:04:20.040
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:21.340
&gt;&gt; Great fun.

00:04:21.340 --> 00:04:22.640
Yeah.

00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:23.940
&gt;&gt; Strange auditorium and
there was no back wall.

00:04:23.940 --> 00:04:25.240
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

