And I think they were pretty
confused about what we were doing.

00:04:34.570 --> 00:04:36.870
&gt;&gt; You know, they got
a little taste of opry.

00:04:36.870 --> 00:04:38.170
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:04:38.170 --> 00:04:39.470
&gt;&gt; We gave them some
opry before the opera.

00:04:39.470 --> 00:04:41.160
&gt;&gt; Right. Different sound.

00:04:41.160 --> 00:04:43.860
I mean, you really do need kind

00:04:43.860 --> 00:04:47.100
of reinforcement I think
in that [inaudible].

00:04:47.100 --> 00:04:48.400
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:50.030
&gt;&gt; Yeah. But the sound
was great there too.

00:04:50.030 --> 00:04:57.280
&gt;&gt; Was your setlist today the
same as what you played last week?

00:04:57.280 --> 00:04:59.110
&gt;&gt; It overlapped.

