It certainly overlapped.

00:05:00.410 --> 00:05:04.340
&gt;&gt; But there's several things
that we had never done before,

00:05:04.340 --> 00:05:07.950
or never done them that way.

00:05:07.950 --> 00:05:11.990
&gt;&gt; Well, I can go through
the set real quickly,

00:05:11.990 --> 00:05:16.930
