out in the greenroom.

00:47:50.470 --> 00:47:54.810
And it's a lovely, lovely tune,
and it's got great challenges,

00:47:54.810 --> 00:47:57.510
all those beautiful
little notes in it.

00:47:57.510 --> 00:47:59.510
I think we're going to
play it some more and more.

00:47:59.510 --> 00:48:01.280
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:48:01.280 --> 00:48:04.210
&gt;&gt; Emmett Lundy recorded as a
part of the road research project

