That's a great unknown
body of material,

00:48:15.120 --> 00:48:17.520
so thanks for bringing it up.

00:48:17.520 --> 00:48:19.520
&gt;&gt; Oh, yeah, that's some
of my favorite stuff.

00:48:19.520 --> 00:48:20.820
&gt;&gt; Yeah?

00:48:20.820 --> 00:48:22.120
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

